The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 48

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

The exterior terraces begin to take shape while changes to the re-do rooms take a smashing. Budgets are tight, so while some work smarter, others work harder. And the Keithenator pulls no punches with a new builder on site.
